:

1. *Od* danas je njegov život postao puno lakši. (From today his life became much easier.)
2. On je *od*mah primetio nekih promena. (He immediately noticed some changes.)
3. Ona je *od*lučila da ode. (She decided to leave.)
4. Oni su *od*lučili da se presele. (They decided to move.)
5. *Od*akle mu je to novac? (Where did he get that money from?)